column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/9d42c3282929ea3dcf9d21ff40e64cd5d5f9b8c3 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated.
